{"id":594832,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/声音如果在沉默中发声是危险的，那首先打破沉默/","date":"2018-09-03T20:33:27Z","modified":"2018-09-03T20:44:55Z","title":"声音|如果在沉默中发声是危险的，那首先打破沉默","content":"<p>一年前，“声音”项目启动，<strong>试图通过公众筹款，来支持一个非虚构创作计划的运行。</strong></p>\n<p>取名“声音”，便是想与这个不断消声的时代“呼应”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-594850\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/1-14-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"167\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/1-14-300x167.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/1-14-768x428.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/1-14.jpg 898w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-594796 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8463-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8463-1-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8463-1-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8463-1.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-594789 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8466-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8466-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8466-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8466.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-594788 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8467-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8467-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8467-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8467.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-594787 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8465-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8465-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8465-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8465.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-594786 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8464-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8464-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8464-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8464.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p>对于创作者和媒体平台来说，这都是一个艰难的时期，资讯市场竞争激烈，大家纷纷抢夺注意力，删文封号愈发常态化，传播变成一场“猫鼠游戏”，也内耗得令人沮丧。此外，还有一直以来的软肋：缺钱。</p>\n<p>“声音”的构想很纯粹，<strong>希望抛开市场和审查的限制，完全以质量和社会价值来评估作品，予以创作者足够的自由度和一定的资金、指导性支持。</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>当然，这是基于创作的角度去谈论“声音”的意义，对于普通社会大众来说，“声音”的意义又在哪里，人们真的需要它吗？</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>这个问题，恐怕只能交给时间来回答了。</p>\n<p>“声音”能做到的，相当有限。在项目发起之时，<strong>我们对“声音”的意义阐述，就是为历史留下一个“今天的存照”。</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>一年过去了，<strong>下面的十篇作品，是2017年至2018年“声音”留下的存照：</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594849\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/2-4-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/2-4-300x190.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/2-4.jpg 557w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1.新建村：一键删除</strong></p>\n<p><strong>2.火灾半年后，被驱逐的磨刀客又回到北京六环外</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594848\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/3-3-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/3-3-300x180.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/3-3-80x48.jpg 80w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/3-3.jpg 535w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>3.实名举报北航教授，受害者们如何推动一场中国版#MeToo</strong><strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594847\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/4-3-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"319\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/4-3-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/4-3.jpg 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>4.新一代访民李宁：用直播twitter和微博记录八年上访路</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594846\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/5-2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/5-2-300x173.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/5-2.jpg 556w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>5.9000瓶污水背后，陕北乡村的魔幻现实</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594845\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/6-2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/6-2-300x180.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/6-2-80x48.jpg 80w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/6-2.jpg 551w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>6.“女声”被消音的100天：没有什么比做activist更令人振奋</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594844\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/7-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/7-1-300x195.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/7-1-230x150.jpg 230w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/7-1.jpg 555w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>6.向死而生：那些自杀热线背后的幸存者</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594843\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/8-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/8-1-300x185.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/8-1-80x48.jpg 80w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/8-1.jpg 556w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>7.告别陶崇园，真相还有多远？</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594842\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/9-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"314\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/9-1-300x171.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/9-1.jpg 519w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>8.合法收养却沦为“黑户”，弃婴陶陶的艰难上学路</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594841\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/91-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/91-300x175.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/91-80x48.jpg 80w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/91.jpg 542w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>9.半年拆掉50余所民办学校，河南周口怎么了？</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594851\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/640-7-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/640-7-300x177.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/640-7-80x48.jpg 80w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/640-7.jpg 535w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></strong></p>\n<p><strong>10.川震十年，“我们的娃娃”还在等一个答案</strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong><strong>添加小编微信号，获取以上十篇作品合集</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-594840 size-thumbnail\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/92-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/92-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/92-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/92-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/92-50x50.jpg 50w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/92.jpg 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>新一期“声音”的筹款活动已经开始，希望能得到你的支持，筹款所得将用于稿件创作与推广、非虚构写作课程。</p>\n<p><strong>扫码立刻支持</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-594789 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8466-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8466-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8466-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/IMG_8466.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-594856 size-full\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/2018-09-03-1111112.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/2018-09-03-1111112.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/2018-09-03-1111112-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/2018-09-03-1111112-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/2018-09-03-1111112-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/index.php?title=404&amp;args=\"><strong>中国数字空间|404博物馆</strong></a></p>\n","author":1052,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[33978,35994,33700,17190,21522,8616]}